"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-life-style-simone-biles-jd-vance-olympics-b2591031.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  In 2021, JD Vance criticized the media for supporting Simone Biles during her 'weakest moment' after withdrawal from Tokyo Olympics  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 225, \"end\": 227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juris_Doctor\", \"score\": 0.8828364669505206, \"rank\": 0.06675384739151687, \"text\": \"JD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juris_Doctor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juris_Doctor\"}, {\"begin\": 228, \"end\": 233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\", \"score\": 0.9999999999799911, \"rank\": 1.9807495307990548e-11, \"text\": \"Vance\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\"}, {\"begin\": 270, \"end\": 282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  An old interview clip featuringJD Vancehas resurfaced shortly afterSimone Bilesmade history at theParis 2024Olympics, in which the potential vice president criticized the media's response towards her withdrawal from the Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 431, \"to\": 690, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On Tuesday, July 31, the 27-year-old athletebecame the most decorated gymnast in American historyafter the women's US gymnastics team scored gold during the all-around finals.\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 867, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 773, \"end\": 781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999992003434741, \"rank\": 7.595886958460362e-07, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 807, \"end\": 809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9989548587597046, \"rank\": 0.0007656788915960273, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The victory marked a comeback for Biles, who withdrew from the last summer Olympics in 2021 due to her mental health.\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 985, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Following her withdrawal from the competition, Vance appeared onFox News'Outnumberedin July 2021, where he called out the media for supporting Biles during her \\\"weakest moment.\\\"\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 1164, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1034, \"end\": 1039, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\", \"score\": 0.9999999999799911, \"rank\": 1.9807495307990548e-11, \"text\": \"Vance\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's understandable that she was going through an incredible amount of pressure,\\\" the Ohio senator said at the time.\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1253, \"end\": 1257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ohio\", \"score\": 0.999441442962045, \"rank\": 0.0005570304424745661, \"text\": \"Ohio\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ohio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ohio\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What I find so weird about this - and it reflects on the media more than it does on Simone Biles - is that we have tried to turn a very tragic moment, Simone Biles quitting the Olympic team, into this act of heroism.\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1501, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1436, \"end\": 1448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I think it reflects pretty poorly on our sort of therapeutic society that we try to praise people not for moments of strength, not for moments of heroism, but for their weakest moments.\\\"\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1694, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Vance continued: \\\"Being an athlete at that level is incredibly tough.\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1765, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A normal response in this moment would be to say: 'It's just a shame that she's going through this.\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1865, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a shame that she quit.'\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1894, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But instead, what our press has done, I think, is turn this into this weird therapeutic moment.\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 1990, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Let us praise her for doing this.'\", \"from\": 1991, \"to\": 2026, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I think that's really where the problem herein lies.\\\"\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2084, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2021, Bilespulled out of the women's all-around gymnastics competitionto focus on her mental health, after suffering from acondition known as the \\\"twisties\\\".\", \"from\": 2086, \"to\": 2246, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The phenomenon, typically experienced by gymnasts, involves losing control mid-air and feeling unable to land the move, creating a high-risk and dangerous situation.\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2412, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles has previously described the twisties as being \\\"lost in the air,\\\" likening the uncomfortable experience to being unable to drive while at the wheel in a car.\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2576, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, that all went away during Tuesday's all-around team final, when Biles scored her eighth Olympic medal - becoming the most decorated gymnast in the US and the fifth-most decorated female Olympic gymnast in the world.\", \"from\": 2578, \"to\": 2802, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2734, \"end\": 2736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9989548587597046, \"rank\": 0.0007656788915960273, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is not the first time that past comments made by Vance have resurfaced sincehe was selected as former president Donald Trump's running matein the 2024 presidential election.\", \"from\": 2804, \"to\": 2982, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2858, \"end\": 2863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\", \"score\": 0.9999999999799911, \"rank\": 1.9807495307990548e-11, \"text\": \"Vance\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\"}, {\"begin\": 2921, \"end\": 2933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.4455366490534854e-14, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 39-year-old Republican politiciansparked outrageafter he described vice president Kamala Harris as a \\\"childless cat lady\\\" during a 2021interviewwithFox Newshost Tucker Carlson.\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 3163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2999, \"end\": 3009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California_Republican_Party\", \"score\": 0.9628167359360341, \"rank\": 0.03168643921690767, \"text\": \"Republican\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California_Republican_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California_Republican_Party\"}, {\"begin\": 3069, \"end\": 3075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kamala_Harris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.470893874601921e-21, \"text\": \"Kamala\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kamala_Harris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kamala_Harris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheHillbilly Elegyauthor claimed that the US was governed by \\\"a bunch of childless cat ladies who are miserable at their own lives and the choices that they have made and so they want to make the rest of the country miserable too.\\\"\", \"from\": 3165, \"to\": 3396, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3207, \"end\": 3209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9989548587597046, \"rank\": 0.0007656788915960273, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Look at Kamala Harris, Pete Buttigieg, AOC, the entire future of the Democrats is controlled by people without children,\\\" Vance said.\", \"from\": 3398, \"to\": 3532, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3407, \"end\": 3413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kamala_Harris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.470893874601921e-21, \"text\": \"Kamala\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kamala_Harris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kamala_Harris\"}, {\"begin\": 3422, \"end\": 3436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pete_Buttigieg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3717214513200702e-20, \"text\": \"Pete Buttigieg\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pete_Buttigieg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pete_Buttigieg\"}, {\"begin\": 3438, \"end\": 3441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandria_Ocasio-Cortez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.426207731623287e-15, \"text\": \"AOC\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandria_Ocasio-Cortez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandria_Ocasio-Cortez\"}, {\"begin\": 3468, \"end\": 3477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California_Democratic_Party\", \"score\": 0.9546437910621297, \"rank\": 0.03024034221983773, \"text\": \"Democrats\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California_Democratic_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California_Democratic_Party\"}, {\"begin\": 3521, \"end\": 3526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\", \"score\": 0.9999999999799911, \"rank\": 1.9807495307990548e-11, \"text\": \"Vance\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"How does it make any sense we have turned our country over to people who do not really have a direct stake in it?\\\"\", \"from\": 3533, \"to\": 3648, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite being selected as Trump's running mate, anotherold video interview showed Vance admittingthat there were \\\"definitely some people\\\" who voted for Trump in 2016 \\\"for racist reasons\\\".\", \"from\": 3650, \"to\": 3837, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3676, \"end\": 3681, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 3.100627459272634e-12, \"text\": \"Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 3802, \"end\": 3807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 3.100627459272634e-12, \"text\": \"Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile,resurfaced emails recently revealedthat Vance once privately considered Trump a \\\"demagogue,\\\" a \\\"disaster,\\\" and a \\\"morally reprehensible human being.\\\"\", \"from\": 3838, \"to\": 3997, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3888, \"end\": 3893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\", \"score\": 0.9999999999799911, \"rank\": 1.9807495307990548e-11, \"text\": \"Vance\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\"}, {\"begin\": 3920, \"end\": 3925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 3.100627459272634e-12, \"text\": \"Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}]}, 